{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_11_02",
  "title": "川咲さくら 2話 伝えたい大切な人",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ダメです～！　何度やってもしっくりこなくて\nこれじゃあドキドキする告白になりません……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No good~! No matter how many times I try‚ it just doesn’t feel right.\nThis won’t turn into a heart-pounding confession…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "このままじゃサニピのみんなだけじゃなくて\nスタッフの人達にも迷惑を掛けちゃう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At this rate‚ I won’t just trouble everyone in Sunny Peace‚\nI’ll cause trouble for the staff too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（あれから何度も練習して、良くはなっている気は）\n（するが、どこかぼんやりした印象が抜けないな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s practiced many times since then‚ and it does feel like it’s improving‚）\n（but there’s still this vague‚ unfocused impression…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "よし。一度、告白の基本に立ち返ってみようか\nまずは好きな人が目の前にいると考えるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. Let’s go back to the basics of a confession.\nFirst‚ imagine the person you like standing right in front of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10799.999999999996,
          "startTime": 40.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "好きな人……好きな人……好きな……ハッ！\nお、思わずよだれが……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someone I like… someone I like… someone I… Hah!\nI-I just started drooling…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さ、さくら？　一体何を想像したんだ？\n俺は好きな人と言ったんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sakura? What exactly were you imagining?\nI said “someone you like”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、すみません！？　お腹が空いちゃってつい\n好きな食べ物を想像しちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I’m sorry!? I got hungry and ended up\nimagining my favorite food.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "思いっきりお腹も鳴っていたな。まぁ、無理をするのも\n良くないし、今日はこれぐらいにしておこうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your stomach was growling pretty loudly too. Well‚\npushing yourself isn’t good—let’s stop here for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今日は頑張ったし、とんかつを食べに行こう\nさくらもだいぶ、その舌になっていそうだしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You worked hard today‚ so let’s go eat tonkatsu.\nSounds like you’re already in the mood for it too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですか！？　このご恩は絶対に忘れません！\n次までに、もーっと勉強しておきます……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!? I’ll never forget this kindness!\nBy next time‚ I’ll study even more…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛とか青春について、今まで以上に\n詳しくなっておきますね！　任せて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll learn even more than before\nabout romance and youth! Leave it to me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "次こそ必ず、最高の告白を届けてみせます！\nまた一緒に練習、よろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next time‚ I’ll definitely deliver the best confession ever!\nLet’s practice together again—please!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0422618551,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1166.6666666000083,
          "startTime": 103.2089285217
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1533.3333333000069,
          "startTime": 103.5755951884
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 103.1755951884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！　私、今度こそ\n告白について一杯勉強してきました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san! This time‚\nI really studied a lot about confessions!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……自信満々なのはありがたいが\n今回はどんな勉強をしてきたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… I appreciate the confidence‚ but\nwhat kind of studying did you do this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛漫画やドラマを沢山観てきました！\n告白シーンが多くて勉強になりましたよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I watched lots of romance manga and dramas!\nThere were so many confession scenes—it was great study!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルのCMを見直して角度以外も調べましたし\nサニピのみんなと告白の練習もしたんですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I rewatched TRINITYAiLE’s CM and looked at more than just the angles‚\nand I even practiced confessions with everyone in Sunny Peace!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "みんなのおかげで、私の拙い演技も\nそれなりに見られるものになったはずです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to everyone‚ even my clumsy acting\nshould be presentable now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あー……そのことなんだが\n実は、メンバーから報告が上がってきていてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh… about that‚ actually—\nsome reports came in from the members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "告白の練習に付き合う中で\nキスの練習もさせられそうになって困った、と……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While practicing confessions‚\nthey almost got roped into practicing kissing‚ which was a problem…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "はい、確かにキッスの練習もしようとしました！\nだって、CMにはそういうシーンもあるんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I did try to practice kissing!\nThere are CMs with scenes like that‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……そういうことか。今回のCMにキスシーンはないぞ\nあるのはあくまでも告白シーンだけだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So that’s it. There’s no kissing scene in this CM.\nThere’s only a confession scene.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "えーーっ！？　キッスシーン、ないんですか！？\nトリエルのCMにはあったのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeeeh!? There’s no kissing scene!?\nBut TRINITYAiLE’s CM had one!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いや、あれはメーカーも違うし\nグループが変わると演出の方向性も変わるからな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that was a different sponsor‚\nand the direction changes depending on the group…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.4333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……！　怜ちゃんにキッスを迫ったけど\nひたすら拒否されたのは、そういうことですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way…! I tried to kiss Rei-chan‚\nand she kept refusing—that’s why!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、みんな悲鳴を上げながら逃げ惑っては\nいましたけど……てっきり照れているのかと……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true everyone was screaming while running away…\nbut I thought they were just embarrassed…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "照れたりするのも、確かに青春っぽくはあるが\n出来れば逃げた時点で気付いてほしかったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being embarrassed does feel youth-like‚ but\nI wish you’d realized once they started running away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "く～っ……！　で、でもでも！　せっかく練習したので\n私のキッス、見ていただいてもいいですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ghh…! B-but still! Since I practiced so hard‚\ncould you watch my kiss anyway!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
