      "text": "いやいやいや！　実際のCMで使わないし\nそれを見せられたとしてどう反応しろというんだ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ no! It won’t be used in the CM‚\nso how am I even supposed to react to that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
