      "text": "そ、そうですよね……うぅ……\nすみません、空回っちゃってばかりで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you’re right… ugh…\nI’m sorry‚ I keep getting ahead of myself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
