      "text": "今回は学校生活や青春がテーマだと聞いて、想像しては\nみたんです。バレンタインデー当日のドキドキ感とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard this time’s theme was school life and youth‚\nso I tried imagining things—like the excitement of Valentine’s Day‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.9999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "誰かと一緒に過ごしたり、部活や学校の行事を\n頑張る中で、好きになっちゃう瞬間とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "spending time with someone‚ and moments where you fall in love\nwhile working hard together in clubs or school events…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.6666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_02-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "でも私、病気のこともあって、学校にはほとんど通えて\nなかったので……。思うほど想像出来てないのかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But because of my illness‚ I could barely attend school‚\nso maybe I can’t imagine it as well as I think…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.4999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
